data.description: Welcome to your new oasis of comfort and convenience, where character meets modern living in the heart of Dahlonega. Boasting 4 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, and a sprawling 2565 square feet of living space, this well-maintained 4-sides brick ranch offers everything you need for a life of luxury.    Step inside to find an abundance of natural light flooding through the many skylights, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere throughout. The master bathroom is a true retreat, featuring a large sunken Jacuzzi tub and a walk-in shower that will leave you feeling pampered and refreshed. Plus, it opens up to a private deck area, perfect for savoring your morning coffee or unwinding after a long day.    With two cozy fireplaces to keep you warm in the winter months, and a basement waiting to be finished into the perfect in-law suite, the possibilities are endless. Plus, the workshop offers plenty of space for DIY projects or storage, with the potential for further improvements.    Conveniently located just minutes from the University of North Georgia, Dahlonega Square, and GA 400, this home offers the perfect blend of privacy and accessibility. Whether you’re searching for an investment property or a place to call home, this is an opportunity you won’t want to miss. Schedule your viewing today before it’s gone!    NOTE: Principals of the seller may share ownership in a licensed real estate brokerage.
